title Retrieve Event Details

actor "Customer" as a
control "<link:_> EventSystem" as s
participant "<link:_>EventService" as u
entity "<link:_>Event" as e
entity "<link:_>Venue" as v
participant "<link:_>AccountService" as c
entity "<link:_>TicketAvailability" as ta
entity "<link:_>TicketQuantity" as tq

note right of a : 1. The administrator wants to retrieve details of a specific event
a -> s : viewEvent(eventName)
activate s

note right of s : 2. The system requests the event details from EventService
s -> u : getEvent(eventName)
activate u

u --> s : event
deactivate u

note right of s : 3. The system displays the event details page
s -> s : displayEventDetailsPage(event)

s --> a :
deactivate s

